				<title>+200!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062029/scp-4420#post-4734482</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 31 Jul 2020 02:59:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Two years, a canon adoption, and a ton of miscellaneous edits later, and here we are.</p> <p>I'm so glad my weird, beautifully big, red magical potato could resonate with so many! I'm betting she's looking down at us all from potato heaven <em>right this second</em> &#8212; or maybe, from somewhere inside <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1689">SCP-1689</a>?</p> <p>It's potato cosmology &#8212; who knows!</p> <p>Anyway, thanks y'all!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
