					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062029#post-3918605</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062029/scp-4420#post-3918605</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 20 Aug 2018 09:36:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I like this, it's weird and funny and sort of sad. I like the whole &quot;concept of a potato&quot; angle and the twist is good. It certainly didn't go where I was expecting it to.</p> <p>I have two minor issues with this; you use the word &quot;spud&quot; a lot but that seems very non-clinical to me (and a quick google has the word tagged as &quot;informal&quot; in its definition for the word). I'd consider replacing it with something else. The other issue is that I'm not into the separated blocks for each specific anomalous effect in your description. I can see why you did it, from a separation of information + text flow point of view, but it just doesn't work for me.</p> <p>Neither of those points are too big though, so +1 from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062029#post-3918568</guid>
				<title>SCP-4420: A Potato Thirst</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062029/scp-4420#post-3918568</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 20 Aug 2018 09:03:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-4420:</strong> A Potato Thirst <strong>[<a href="https://youtu.be/zaW6ApXbHq4">Audio version</a>]</strong><br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>My first article since Doomcon!</p> <p>The title of this article &#8212; A Potato Thirst &#8212; is based on a misspelling of &quot;Apotheosis&quot;. In fact, that's the entire reason for this article. This article was also written with the intention of it placing under 500 words, so this is my shortest article by far.</p> <p><strong>UPDATE:</strong> This article is now a part of the <strong>Apotheosis Canon</strong>! Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1436137&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="fieldstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1436137)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fieldstone" >fieldstone</a></span> for making it work.</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;and&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span><br /> ▶ HumidHermit (account deleted)<br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/secretcrow" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3604422&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="SecretCrow" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3604422)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/secretcrow" >SecretCrow</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gibbyfuckingdies" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2200357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1595787318" alt="GibbyFuckingDies" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2200357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gibbyfuckingdies" >GibbyFuckingDies</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a